# 🎨 Salati — Visily Prompts (مقسّمة — كل واحد أقل من 4000 حرف)

> كل برومبت لشاشة واحدة. انسخ كل واحد لوحده في Visily.

---

## Prompt 1: Main Dashboard (الشاشة الرئيسية)

```
Design a Windows desktop app main screen for "Salati" — an Islamic prayer reminder.

Style: Dark mode, premium, Islamic-inspired, calm.
Colors: Background #0D1117, Cards #161B22, Green accent #1B8A6B, Gold accent #C8A96E, Text #E6EDF3, Muted #8B949E.
Borderless window with custom title bar. Rounded corners 12px. Size: 700x500px.

TITLE BAR (top):
Left: Mosque icon + "Salati" in gold.
Right buttons: 📌 pin, ⚙️ settings, 🌙 theme, "AR" language, — minimize, ✕ close. Small and minimal.

HERO SECTION (center, 40% height):
Large card with green border glow containing:
- Large prayer emoji: 🌤️
- "صلاة العصر" large white text
- "Asr Prayer" small muted text below
- "03:45 PM" in gold color
- Giant countdown: "01:23:45" — 32px, white, monospace
- Thin green progress bar below (72% filled)
- "متبقي | Remaining" tiny muted text

5 PRAYER CARDS ROW (below hero, horizontal):
5 cards evenly spaced, each ~110x90px:
- 🌅 الفجر 04:35 — gray, ✅ (passed)
- ☀️ الظهر 12:15 — gray, ✅ (passed)
- 🌤️ العصر 03:45 — GREEN BORDER GLOW, ⏳ (next prayer, highlighted)
- 🌇 المغرب 06:30 — normal dark, ⌛ (upcoming)
- 🌙 العشاء 08:00 — normal dark, ⌛ (upcoming)

BOTTOM BAR:
"📅 Saturday, April 12, 2026" left. "📍 Cairo, Egypt" center. "▼ Minimize to Tray" right subtle text.

Faint Islamic geometric pattern at 3% opacity in background. Premium, calm, spiritual feel.
```

