## Prompt 2: Settings Panel (لوحة الإعدادات)

```
Design a settings slide panel for "Salati" prayer reminder desktop app.

Style: Dark mode panel sliding from right side over a blurred/dimmed main screen.
Colors: Panel bg #161B22, green accent #1B8A6B, gold #C8A96E, text #E6EDF3, muted #8B949E.
Panel width: 350px, full height. Left green border glow. Rounded left corners.

PANEL TOP:
"⚙️ الإعدادات | Settings" title in white. "✕" close button.

LEFT EDGE — 4 vertical tabs:
🕐 المواعيد (Prayer Times) — ACTIVE with green indicator
🔔 التنبيهات (Alerts)
🎨 المظهر (Appearance)
⚙️ عام (General)

CONTENT — Prayer Times tab showing:

Source selection:
(●) تلقائي | Auto (API) — selected
( ) إدخال يدوي | Manual

Location dropdowns (dark inputs, green focus):
- الدولة | Country: [Egypt ▾]
- المدينة | City: [Cairo ▾]
- طريقة الحساب | Method: [Egyptian Authority ▾]
- Green button: "🔄 تحديث | Refresh"

Manual input section (shown when Manual selected):
5 time picker rows:
🌅 الفجر: [04:35 AM]
☀️ الظهر: [12:15 PM]
🌤️ العصر: [03:45 PM]
🌇 المغرب: [06:30 PM]
🌙 العشاء: [08:00 PM]

Bottom: Green gradient "💾 حفظ | Save" button.

Behind the panel: the main dashboard screen blurred at 40% opacity.
```

