## Prompt 3: Settings — Alerts Tab (تنبيهات)

```
Design an alerts settings panel for "Salati" prayer app.

Dark slide panel, 350px wide. Bg #161B22, green #1B8A6B, gold #C8A96E, text #E6EDF3.
This is the "🔔 Alerts" tab content inside the settings panel.

Title: "🔔 التنبيهات | Alerts"

PER-PRAYER ALERT TABLE (5 rows):
Each row has: [Icon+Name] [Toggle] [Minutes dropdown] [Sound dropdown]

🌅 الفجر    [✅ ON]  [10 min ▾]  [أذان الحرم ▾]
☀️ الظهر    [✅ ON]  [5 min ▾]   [أذان الحرم ▾]
🌤️ العصر    [✅ ON]  [5 min ▾]   [أذان الحرم ▾]
🌇 المغرب   [✅ ON]  [10 min ▾]  [أذان الحرم ▾]
🌙 العشاء   [✅ ON]  [5 min ▾]   [أذان الحرم ▾]

Toggles: Green when ON, gray when OFF. Rounded switch style.
Dropdowns: Dark bg #0D1117, subtle border.

SOUND SETTINGS section below:
- Volume slider: [████████░░] 80% — green fill
- Toggle: "تنبيه وقت الأذان | Alert at Adhan time" [ON]
- Dropdown: "نوع التنبيه | Type" [صوت أذان | Adhan Sound ▾]

Bottom: Green gradient "💾 حفظ | Save" button.

Clean spacing, professional toggle switches, dark input fields with green focus borders.
```

