## Prompt 4: Alert Popup (نافذة التنبيه)

```
Design a prayer alert popup notification for "Salati" desktop app.

Size: 420x300px. Borderless, rounded corners 16px, drop shadow.
Position: Top-right of screen. Always on top.
Bg: #161B22 with 2px green (#1B8A6B) gradient border glow.

LAYOUT (centered, vertical):

Top: Thin Islamic geometric decorative line (green/gold, subtle).

Center content:
- Large prayer emoji: 🌤️ with subtle green radial glow behind it
- Line 1: "تبقى 10 دقائق على" — medium white text
- Line 2: "صلاة العصر" — LARGE bold white text (24px)
- Line 3: "03:45 PM" — gold color (#C8A96E)
- Spacer
- "حي على الصلاة حي على الفلاح" — small, muted, italic
- Thin green divider line

Bottom buttons (two, side by side):
- Left: "🔇 كتم | Mute" — outline style, subtle border, no fill
- Right: "✅ تم | Dismiss" — green gradient button (#1B8A6B to #C8A96E)

Tiny text at very bottom: "يختفي تلقائياً بعد 60 ثانية" — very muted, 10px

Feel: Gentle, calm, beautiful. A spiritual reminder, not an aggressive popup.
Subtle shadow around the entire window.
```

