## Prompt 5: Widget Mode + Splash Screen

```
Design 2 screens for "Salati" prayer app:

SCREEN A — WIDGET MODE (compact strip):
Size: 300x85px. Borderless, rounded 12px, always on top.
Background: rgba(13,17,23,0.92) — dark, slightly transparent.
1px green (#1B8A6B) subtle border glow.

Horizontal layout, 3 sections:
- Left: 🌤️ emoji + "العصر" text + "03:45 PM" in gold below
- Center: Large "01:23:45" countdown in white monospace. Tiny green progress bar below.
- Right: 📌 pin button + ✕ close button (small, minimal)

Feels like a floating mini player — minimal, always visible, not distracting.

---

SCREEN B — SPLASH SCREEN:
Size: 480x340px. Borderless, centered, no taskbar.
Background: Gradient from #0A0E14 (top) to #0D1117 (bottom).

Center layout:
- Faint green radial glow in center (very subtle, like light behind mosque)
- Mosque silhouette icon — simple, modern geometric style, green (#1B8A6B)
- "Salati" — large elegant font, gold (#C8A96E)
- "صلاتي" — Arabic, slightly smaller, white
- Spacer
- "وَأَقِيمُوا الصَّلَاةَ" — subtle gold, muted
- Bottom: Thin green progress bar (loading animation)
- "v1.0" — tiny muted gray text, bottom-right

Premium, spiritual, calm branding moment. No window controls.
```

