## Prompt 6: System Tray Menu

```
Design a system tray context menu for "Salati" prayer app.

Style: Windows 11 dark context menu. Size: ~220x220px.
Bg: #1C2128, rounded corners 8px, subtle shadow.
Text: #E6EDF3 primary, #8B949E muted.

Menu items (top to bottom):

"🕌 Salati" — bold, gold (#C8A96E), header, not clickable

── thin separator line (#2D333B) ──

"⏳ العصر: 03:45 PM" — green text (#1B8A6B)
"     متبقي: 01:23:45" — muted, indented, smaller

── separator ──

"📂 فتح Salati | Open" — white text, hover: subtle green bg
"📌 وضع مصغر | Widget" — white text
"🔕 كتم مؤقت | Mute" — white text, toggle indicator
"⚙️ الإعدادات | Settings" — white text

── separator ──

"❌ خروج | Exit" — red text (#E06C75)

Hover effect: subtle green (#1B8A6B) at 10% opacity background.
Each item has 8px padding. Icons left-aligned.
Compact, clean, modern Windows 11 style.
```

